HEADWORD: Incandescence
<hw>In`can*des"cence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>incandescence</ets>.]</ety> <def>A white heat, or the glowing or
luminous whiteness of a body caused by intense heat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

